00:51:38.280 --> 00:51:40.639
Sports is interesting in that it has a season concept.

00:51:40.639 --> 00:51:43.639
So, it actually ends up being like,

00:51:43.639 --> 00:51:46.080
in this case, it evaluates each kind of season

00:51:46.080 --> 00:51:47.000
