of what is done in sports analytics, right?

00:56:06.600 --> 00:56:10.840
So Mitch, for example, and myself have worked for teams

00:56:10.840 --> 00:56:12.959
and you want to have values on players

00:56:12.959 --> 00:56:16.159
because it's really important for how much you,

00:56:16.159 --> 00:56:19.080
who you should draft, who you should sign,

